                <p>Founded in 1998, our bakery has been a cornerstone of the community for over two decades. We believe in using traditional baking techniques and high-quality, locally sourced ingredients to create baked goods that bring joy to our customers. Our mission is to share our passion for fresh, delicious food with every loaf of bread, every pastry, and every custom cake we bake.</p>
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x400?text=Our+Bakery+Team" alt="Our bakery team">
